data.description: Newly renovated kitchen and bathrooms. Move right in and enjoy year round living or weekend get-a-ways in "the Colony". This beautiful 3000sq/ft contemporary is situated at the end of a private driveway.  Surrounded by nature trails, with lake rights offering swimming & boating, volleyball, clubhouse and summer camp for the kids. Walk to Goldens Bridge Train. One mile to 684 and less than 1 hour to NYC. Open floor plan with hardwood floors, high ceilings, a wall of windows for amazing sunlight in the afternoon, custom wood burning stove and private outdoor deck.
